She said after the completion of the Ram Temple, the next step would be to work towards a â€˜Ram Rajyaâ€™, for which Prime Minister Narendra Modi is â€œrelentlesslyâ€ working. â€œRam Temple was a struggle for spine (self-respect), Ram Rajya would be struggle for stomachâ€¦ The country is lucky that Modi is PM, who has all capability to take us towards that,â€ she said.

